ckquote>推</blockquote><br />\n感謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba589e09f5406d29084184343a07b2fdb0ec511","tid":321174,"uid":43843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:38:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/323667?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/323667?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n行左幾個地方未發現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4472c6735d193b3545009e60b038fdbca33396d5","tid":321174,"uid":64034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:55:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/323667?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/323667?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n行左幾個地方未發現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我琴晚 差唔多打曬九龍的24小時麥當勞...打咗40間有多.. 有人打港島區的....要求幫眼睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留曬電話.... 都冇電話到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我應該識你.... 大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望快啲搵番<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特別感謝麥當勞員工 耐心聆聽我的描述和幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3653f7ab410675cbad1fdd37453b2ed0eb5592cb","tid":321174,"uid":68681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:57:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac0a0eba99c4ddb0ef506601519c89da9831aa54","tid":321174,"uid":64034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:59:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推</blockquote><br />\n感謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53bad6820c910872cea19247d43c575814b1ad5","tid":321174,"uid":100983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T01:14:37.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}